```plantuml
@startuml GoogleCloudPlatform_gke-pubsub-websocket-adapter
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor WebClient

rectangle GKE #lightblue {
  rectangle "pulltop" as Pulltop #lightgreen
  rectangle "websocketd" as WebSocketD #lightyellow
  rectangle "Ephemeral\nPOSIX Storage" as EphemeralStorage #aliceblue
}

rectangle "Google Cloud\nPub/Sub" as PubSub #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
WebClient --> WebSocketD : Connect via WebSocket
WebSocketD --> EphemeralStorage : Buffer recent messages
WebSocketD --> Pulltop : Request latest messages
Pulltop --> PubSub : Pull messages from topic
PubSub --> Pulltop : Deliver messages
Pulltop --> EphemeralStorage : Store messages temporarily
WebSocketD --> WebClient : Stream messages in real-time
@enduml
```